quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,25,"Weltin ɓeen goonɗinɓe ɓe ngolli moƴƴi wonde ɓeɓ keɓa aljannaaji caalli na ndonga les majji kala nde ɓe njeɗaa toon ɓiɓɓe leɗɗe ɓe mbi'a ko ɗee min njeɗanoo ko adii, kono si ɓe meeɗii ɗe ɓe tawa eɗe ceerti, eɓe keɓa toon rewɓe laaɓɓe ɓe ñiiɓida toon. @Corrected"
  2,26,"Alla aamantaa addude yeru hay so wonii wano ɓowngu e ko ɓuri ɗum, so tawii ko goonɗinɓe eɓe nganndi ko goonga iwɗo e Jooma maɓɓe, so tawii ko yedduɓe ɓe mbi'a holko Alla yiɗi e oo yeru Ombo majjina heewɓe O feewna heen heewɓe, alaa majjinteeɗo heen sonaa yaltuɓe ɗoftaare. @Corrected"
  2,27,Ɓeen firtooɓe aadi Alla ɓaawo tiiɗneede mbo eɓe taƴa ko Alla yamiri yo jokke eɓe mbonna ka lesdi ko kamɓe ngoni rusɓiiɓe (pertuɓe)
  2,28,Holno njeddirton Alla tawa ngoodaano O wuurni on rewa heen O wara on rewa heen O wuurtina on ɓaawo ɗuum ko e Makko nduttoto-ɗon
  2,29,Kanko tagani on kala ko woni e lesdi ndi ɓaawo ɗuum O faandii asamaan O fotndi mbo asamaanji jeeɗiɗi Kanko gannduɗo kala huunde. @Corrected